text: Nemaschema parteflavoantennatum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1969.BioLib.cz - Nemaschema parteflavoantennatum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1969
